lead_paragraph: Jose Fernandez tied a career high with 14 strikeouts, overshadowing Clayton Kershaw's return from injury and leading the Miami Marlins to a 4-1 win over the Los Angeles Dodgers on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Fernandez Spoils Kershaw's Return, Marlins Top Dodgers 4-1
